snippet.description:
Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 
Mario Maker: 7th Grade NIGHTMARE! ►► http://bit.ly/1m88Fj2
Will You Press The Button?! ►► http://bit.ly/1RSsGX7

I've already bested a handful of Rubberross's Mario Maker levels but it was clear YOU still wanted more. The battle between Rubberross and myself really starts to heat up as I take on some of his more difficult levels. All while discussing some of our most hated Mario villains. 

Follow all the updates on new episodes of GTLive!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
